title: ANGRAU Notification 2026 - Walk-in interview for Medical Officer Posts
description: The Acharya NG Ranga Agricultural University (ANGRAU) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Medical Officer Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MBBS can apply for the ANGRAU Notification 2026. The interested applicants can attend the walk-in interview.
